Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:44.85,RESET OP CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}令未來循聲而至
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:55.74,RESET OP CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}我駐足叩問內心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:01:03.54,RESET OP CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}世界將如何展現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:15.30,RESET OP CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}在理想與現實的罅隙之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:25.73,RESET OP CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}時鐘的指針便從此處踏步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.31,0:01:34.61,RESET OP CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}為了抹去過去的傷痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:45.50,RESET OP CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}從漆黑樓梯上  疾走而下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:53.84,RESET OP CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}為了將珍視之物守護
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:02:07.77,RESET OP CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}我願念出誓言  與你相逢
